Mathematical Formulae  

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[440, 138, 561, 154]]<|/det|>
## 1. ALGEBRA  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[83, 169, 242, 185]]<|/det|>
Quadratic Equation  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[120, 198, 387, 215]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^{2} + bx + c = 0\) ,  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[418, 216, 582, 250]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^{2} - 4ac}}{2a}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[83, 275, 230, 290]]<|/det|>
Binomial Theorem  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[247, 295, 753, 331]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1}b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2}b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r}b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[120, 348, 490, 383]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n - r)!r!}\)  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[83, 413, 390, 430]]<|/det|>
Arithmetic series \(u_{n} = a + (n - 1)d\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[249, 437, 536, 468]]<|/det|>
\[S_{n} = \frac{1}{2} n(a + l) = \frac{1}{2} n\{2a + (n - 1)d\}\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[83, 490, 193, 505]]<|/det|>
Geometric series  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[249, 488, 430, 576]]<|/det|>
\[u_{n} = a r^{n - 1}\] \[S_{n} = \frac{a(1 - r^{n})}{1 - r} (r\neq 1)\] \[S_{\infty} = \frac{a}{1 - r} (|r|< 1)\]  

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[404, 614, 597, 630]]<|/det|>
## 2. TRIGONOMETRY  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[83, 646, 159, 661]]<|/det|>
Identities  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[419, 673, 585, 723]]<|/det|>
\[\frac{\sin^{2}A + \cos^{2}A = 1}{\sec^{2}A = 1 + \tan^{2}A\] \[\cos \mathrm{e}^{2}A = 1 + \cot^{2}A\]  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[83, 769, 244, 785]]<|/det|>
Formulae for \(\Delta ABC\)  

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[405, 794, 598, 880]]<|/det|>
\[\frac{a}{\sin A} = \frac{b}{\sin B} = \frac{c}{\sin C\] \[a^{2} = b^{2} + c^{2} - 2bc\cos A\] \[\Delta = \frac{1}{2} bc\sin A\]<｜end▁of▁sentence｜>
